I brought you some late-night snacks.

5
00:00:57,334 --> 00:00:59,754
Did you get hurt?

6
00:00:59,754 --> 00:01:02,634
I bumped into something accidentally. It's nothing.

7
00:01:03,834 --> 00:01:06,180
Come in. Let me apply some medicine.

8
00:01:06,180 --> 00:01:07,550
Okay.

9
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:19,754
Do you know something? As a child, I studied wrestling for a while.

10
00:01:19,754 --> 00:01:22,194
