12
00:01:30,094 --> 00:01:31,708
I'm sorry.

13
00:01:32,710 --> 00:01:35,914
Don't worry, I didn't suffer.

14
00:01:35,914 --> 00:01:40,214
It's just a pity I couldn't give him more punches to vent frustration on your behalf.

15
00:01:42,434 --> 00:01:44,814
Why are you helping me?

16
00:01:50,754 --> 00:01:54,474
Because I want to have an ordinary, warm family.

17
00:01:55,474 --> 00:02:00,354
In my dreams, my ideal wife resonates with me intellectually.

18
00:02:00,354 --> 00:02:04,194
And in life, we can depend on one another.

19
00:02:04,194 --> 00:02:06,394
We can laugh together during happy times

20
00:02:06,394 --> 00:02:10,954
and hug each other when we're tired.

21
00:02:13,874 --> 00:02:19,074
And... you are the embodiment of my dream.

22
00:02:22,154 --> 00:02:25,234
That's because you don't know me yet.

23
00:02:25,234 --> 00:02:29,160
I'm very different from that person you imagine.

24
00:02:30,054 --> 00:02:32,874
I'll get to know you starting now.

25
00:02:39,974 --> 00:02:43,534
- Hello? 
  - Director Bai, bad news. You should hurry back.

26
00:02:43,534 --> 00:02:46,274
Don't be anxious. I'll come over now.

27
00:02:48,234 --> 00:02:51,534
I need to return to work. Something came up at the company.

28
00:02:53,954 --> 00:02:56,260
- Drive safely. 
 - Okay.

29
00:03:01,830 --> 00:03:04,280
 You shouldn't have stopped me. I landed only one punch.

30
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:06,350
